/ch_qos_reload4j/reload4j/ZeroConfSupportTest.java`\n\nWhat was added:\n- A second test path that loads an isolated copy of `ZeroConfSupport` with a JmDNS v1-style API:\n  - `JmDNS` has a public no-arg constructor and no `create()` method.\n  - `ServiceInfo` exposes the v1 constructor expected by reload4j.\n- This should reach the remaining uncovered call sites:\n  - `Class#newInstance()` in `createJmDNSVersion1`\n  - `Class#getConstructor(...)` in `buildServiceInfoVersion1`\n  - `Constructor#newInstance(...)` in `buildServiceInfoVersion1`\n- The dynamic-loading path catches `Error` and verifies Native Image unsupported dynamic class loading via `NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(error)` as required.\n\nPer instruction, I did not compile or run tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c77dd3e4a71f1640169f4fd97288481a09505f7559ec64dde\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 594, "output": 579, "cacheRead": 57344, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 58517, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777663374532, "responseId": "resp_0c77dd3e4a71f1640169f4fd8f1d3881a0a2e9fc46a0ad69be"}}
